<quantity box="[237,351,961,988]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.2" metricValueMax="9.5" metricValueMin="0.9" pageId="18" pageNumber="34" unit="mm" value="52.0" valueMax="95.0" valueMin="9.0">9–95 mm</quantity>
long, approximately the same size or longer than the ovary; rostellum mid-lobe mostly held beyond the anther loculi ............................................................................................................ 2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
